A lot of times I'm not coming or very late it's because I feel complete shit in the morning and need a lot of time to normalize and boot myself up into normal. Eating properly will make my general well-being better and so it will consume less energy to be alive. One of the reasons I'm trying to put down cigarettes is because it also contributes to this problem and I feel better since I reduced to 3-4 a day.

4. Prioritize: Pretty self-explanatory. If I can play games and have to do something I will do the work first. This is the hardest to uphold as it is very easy to slip with this, but I will try to do it. It will probably act more of a guideline for me, rather than a rule.
